                        we believe that dining is not just a meal—it’s an event to savor and share. Step into our world,
                        where every detail is designed to delight.
                    </p>
                    <img src="https://food.fnr.sndimg.com/content/dam/images/food/fullset/2022/09/07/FNK_Charcuterie-board-how-to_step-13.jpg.rend.hgtvcom.1280.720.suffix/1662570515845.jpeg"
