                            </strong>
                        </p>
                    </div>

                </div>
                <!-- RIGHT COLUMN -->
                <div class="col s12 m6">
                    <p class="description" style="font-size: 19px;">
                        Whether you’re here for a romantic evening or a gathering with friends, La Table offers a refined yet
                        cozy ambiance. Every dish is a testament to our dedication to quality and tradition. Join us for a culinary
                        journey that’s as delightful as it is authentic. Our attentive staff is here to ensure your experience is
                        seamless and memorable. From the flicker of candlelight to the aroma of freshly baked bread, every moment
                        at La Table is designed to enchant. Discover a place where the love for food and community comes together
                        in perfect harmony.
                    </p>
                    <img src="https://www.shutterstock.com/image-photo/desserts-pastries-tempting-delightful-spread-600nw-2425678879.jpg"
                         alt="French Appetizers"
                         class="responsive-img"
